\begin{itemize}[leftmargin=1.5em, itemsep=0.2em]
    \item Leading post-training of OpenAI's frontier model (\textbf{GPT-5.4/5.4 mini}) in an internal restricted-access project with authorized access to OpenAI models, code, and technical assets to drive agentic productivity capabilities across long-horizon office tasks, deep research, and collaborative authoring.
    \item Leading the science for \textbf{Agent Mode} in M365/Office — designing agentic pipelines with comprehensive tool coverage across the full suite of Office capabilities, enabling multi-step, tool-augmented task execution at scale.    \item Representing the organization in regular executive briefings to Microsoft CEO \textit{Satya Nadella} and EVP \textit{Rajesh Jha}, communicating post-training and agent mode strategy and roadmap at the SLT level.
